Package: deepagentsr
Title: Deep-Agents-Style Agent Harness for R
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Hadi", "Master", , "hadi@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides an R-native agent harness inspired by Deep Agents,
    with model adapters, tool metadata, virtual filesystems, planning tools,
    subagents, skills, memory, human approval, permissions, and event traces.
